  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU:</h1><p><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1178000/extras/1c5c776f88be1de1457f7c83e4c3ddfb.avif?t=1679761864\" width=800 height=170 /></span><br><br>Collect, teleport, become a ghost and beat another level within the same world. Can you do this job?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1178000/extras/1cdfa3ecdd25a5943fb43913f7349ca9.poster.avif?t=1679761864\" width=500 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1178000/extras/1cdfa3ecdd25a5943fb43913f7349ca9.webm?t=1679761864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1178000/extras/1cdfa3ecdd25a5943fb43913f7349ca9.mp4?t=1679761864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><br><br>● More than 125 hand craft levels for you to BEAT and be the BEST.<br>● Explore more than 20 different worlds with specific challenges for each one.<br>● Teleport and accelerate when necessary, but be careful not to crash.<br>● Super-rigid control schemes designed for controllers and also keyboards.<br>● Exclusive soundtrack composed by the developer himself.<br>● Deep story told by poems.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1178000/extras/1c5c776f88be1de1457f7c83e4c3ddfb.avif?t=1679761864\" width=800 height=170 /></span><br><br>Collect, teleport, become a ghost and beat another level within the same world. Can you do this job?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1178000/extras/1cdfa3ecdd25a5943fb43913f7349ca9.poster.avif?t=1679761864\" width=500 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1178000/extras/1cdfa3ecdd25a5943fb43913f7349ca9.webm?t=1679761864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1178000/extras/1cdfa3ecdd25a5943fb43913f7349ca9.mp4?t=1679761864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><br><br>● More than 125 hand craft levels for you to BEAT and be the BEST.<br>● Explore more than 20 different worlds with specific challenges for each one.<br>● Teleport and accelerate when necessary, but be careful not to crash.<br>● Super-rigid control schemes designed for controllers and also keyboards.<br>● Exclusive soundtrack composed by the developer himself.<br>● Deep story told by poems.",
